# Library Constants & Utilities

Check these before defining new constants or helpers. All in `@/lib/`.

## Card Gradients (`ui-gradients.ts`)
```typescript
import { CARD_GRADIENTS } from "@/lib/ui-gradients";
// Keys: slate, emerald, sky, violet, rose, amber
<div className={`pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 ${CARD_GRADIENTS.emerald}`} />
```

## Guestbook (`guestbook-constants.ts`, `guestbook-ownership.ts`)
- `COLOR_OPTIONS` — color choices for guestbook cards
- `DEFAULT_COLOR`, `getGradientForColor(color)`
- `getOwnedEntries()`, `saveOwnedEntry(id, token)`, `removeOwnedEntry(id)`, `getTokenForEntry(id)`, `getOwnedIds()`

## Todos (`todo-constants.ts`)
- `KANBAN_COLUMNS` — column definitions for Kanban board
- `RECURRING_OPTIONS` — recurring task frequency options

## Adventures (`adventure-constants.tsx`)
- `ADVENTURE_SEASONS`, `ADVENTURE_CATEGORIES`
- `getSeasonInfo(season)`, `getCategoryInfo(category)`, `getAdventureSeasons(adventure)`

## Gallery (`gallery-constants.tsx`)
- `SEASONS`, `ACTIVITIES`
- `getSeasonIcon(season)`, `getActivityLabel(activity)`

## Expenses (`expense-utils.ts`)
- `getCategoryLabel`, `getSubcategoryLabel`, `getCategoryIcon`, `getCategoryGradient`
- `formatExpenseDate`, `formatExpenseDateShort`

## Loons (`loon-utils.ts`)
- `getNestingLabel`, `getWeatherLabel`, `getWindLabel`, `getBehaviorLabel`, `getDisturbanceLabel`
- `formatLoonDate`, `getTotalLoons`, `deriveSavedLocations`, `getNestingGradient`

## Blog (`blog-utils.ts`)
- `formatDate`, `formatLongDate`, `formatShortDate`, `wasEdited`

## General (`utils.ts`)
- `cn()` — `clsx` + `tailwind-merge` for conditional classes

## Announcement (`announcement.ts`)
- `ANNOUNCEMENT` config object for the top banner

## Auth Client (`auth-client.ts`)
- `authClient` — better-auth React client for `useSession()`, `signIn`, `signOut`

## Server Data Fetching
- `guestbook-server.ts` → `getGuestbookData()`
- `puzzle-server.ts` → `getPuzzleData()`
- `todos-server.ts` → `getTodosServer()`
- `expenses-server.ts` → `getExpensesServer()`
- `blog-server.ts` → `fetchPosts()`, `fetchPostBySlug()`, `fetchOtherPosts()`
- `adventures-server.ts` → `fetchAdventureById()`, `fetchOtherAdventures()`
- `loon-server.ts` → `getLoonData()`
